page.title: 12SCHOOL
page.content: My school you could say, is big. It's name is Catford County School. Sometimes Catford Boys want to mix with us, but we put up a fight and we win. I like some of my teachers. The lesson I have are English, Music, Science, Art, Geography, German, History, Needlework, Games, RE, Computer Studies. The lesson I like most is Maths, Game, History, the first floor is red the second floor is brown and the third floor is green,and there are about 50 classes on each floor. There is a park next to our school and it is called FORSTER PARK. School is very good for you because you can get a job when you are older.
